<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ٨ الى ٩]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَمَّا مَنْ جاءَكَ يَسْعى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> وَهُوَ يَخْشى <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَّا مَنْ جاءَكَ يَسْعى:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَسْعى يسرع لطلب العلم والهداية.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ يَخْشى:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أي وهو يخاف الله.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ١٠ الى ١٦]<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَأَنْتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> كَلاَّ إِنَّها تَذْكِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> فَمَنْ شاءَ ذَكَرَهُ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> فِي صُحُفٍ مُكَرَّمَةٍ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> مَرْفُوعَةٍ مُطَهَّرَةٍ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بِأَيْدِي سَفَرَةٍ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span> كِرامٍ بَرَرَةٍ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٠-<span class="c5"> فَأَنْتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّى:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَلَهَّى تتشاغل.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١١-<span class="c5"> كَلَّا إِنَّها تَذْكِرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كَلَّا حقا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>إِنَّها إن هذه الآيات.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تَذْكِرَةٌ عظة.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١٢-<span class="c5"> فَمَنْ شاءَ ذَكَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ذَكَرَهُ أي القرآن واتعظ به.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١٣-<span class="c5"> فِي صُحُفٍ مُكَرَّمَةٍ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فِي صُحُفٍ هو فى صحف.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مُكَرَّمَةٍ عند الله.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>١٤-<span class="c5"> مَرْفُوعَةٍ مُطَهَّرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>مُطَهَّرَةٍ منزهة عن كل نقص.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>١٥-<span class="c5"> بِأَيْدِي سَفَرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>سَفَرَةٍ ملائكة جعلهم الله سفراء بينه وبين رسله.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>١٦-<span class="c5"> كِرامٍ بَرَرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>كِرامٍ أخيار.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>بَرَرَةٍ محسنين.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>